VARDESC: Arm used to measure mid upper arm circumference.
Distance from the spine extending from acromion process to tip of the olecranon process measured to the nearest 0.1 centimeter.
Midpoint of the distance from the spine extending from acromion process to tip of the olecranon process measured to the nearest 0.1 centimeter.
Arm circumference measured at the midpoint of the distance from the spine extending from acromion process to tip of the olecranon process measured to the nearest 0.1 centimeter.
